cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning features and probabilistic models for multi-object classification and scene understanding in natural images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves probabilistic models (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with image datasets.
